## Verification Plan

### Automated
- None (no test suite exists)

### Manual
1. In Payment Management, click **Record Payment** → select a team that already has a payment → confirm the form pre-fills with existing values and shows a warning banner
2. Save → verify only one record exists in the table (no duplicate row)
3. Click the **History** button → verify a log entry shows the action, before/after amounts and status, timestamp and admin name
4. Edit an existing payment → change amount → save → verify the history now has two entries for that payment

