## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Confirmation UX**: When a user clicks "+ Record Payment" and selects a team that already has a payment, should the system:
> - **(A) Auto-detect and pre-fill** silently (just show a yellow warning banner in the form), or
> - **(B) Show a confirmation dialog** before proceeding?
